<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 03:23:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国加强政策措施捍卫脆弱的人民币</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-steps-up-policy-measures-defend-fragile-yuan-2025-01-13/</link><description>周一，在人民币兑强势美元徘徊于16个月低点附近之际，中国加大了政策措施力度，放宽允许更多离岸借款的规定，并发出口头警告，以捍卫人民币疲软。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 03:08:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-steps-up-policy-measures-defend-fragile-yuan-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>韩国和日本外长将在首尔政治动荡中会面</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-japan-foreign-ministers-meet-amid-political-turmoil-seoul-2025-01-13/</link><description>韩国和日本外长将于周一在韩国首都举行会谈，美国的主要盟友寻求在首尔数十年来最严重的政治危机中强调改善关系和共同的安全担忧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 03:03:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-japan-foreign-ministers-meet-amid-political-turmoil-seoul-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲足球周</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/week-asian-football-2025-01-13/</link><description>本周亚洲足球的谈话要点：</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 02:51:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/week-asian-football-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>开发商收到清算申请后中国世茂股价下跌15%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-shimao-drops-15-after-developer-receives-liquidation-petition-2025-01-13/</link><description>在收到清算申请后，中国世茂集团的股价周一下跌 15%，至 0.73 港元，为 9 月 26 日以来的最低水平。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 01:51:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-shimao-drops-15-after-developer-receives-liquidation-petition-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>马尼拉表示，日本、菲律宾和美国誓言深化合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/japan-philippines-us-vow-deepen-cooperation-manila-says-2025-01-13/</link><description>马尼拉周一在领导人通话后表示，面对地区水域日益紧张的局势，日本、菲律宾和美国誓言根据三边安排进一步加强关系。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 01:43:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/japan-philippines-us-vow-deepen-cooperation-manila-says-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>美国加强制裁以遏制俄罗斯向中国和印度供应石油</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/tougher-us-sanctions-curb-russian-oil-supply-china-india-2025-01-12/</link><description>中国和印度炼油厂将从中东、非洲和美洲采购更多石油，从而推高价格和运输成本。</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 11:59:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/tougher-us-sanctions-curb-russian-oil-supply-china-india-2025-01-12/</guid></item><item><title>央行行长潘基文在京会见英国央行总裁贝利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-central-bank-governor-pan-meets-boes-bailey-beijing-2025-01-12/</link><description>中国央行周日表示，中国人民银行行长潘功胜周六在北京会见了英国央行行长安德鲁·贝利，讨论了金融稳定与合作等话题。</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 04:42:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-central-bank-governor-pan-meets-boes-bailey-beijing-2025-01-12/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国黑客威胁的加剧，拜登将下令实施更严格的网络安全标准</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/china-hacking-threat-builds-biden-order-tougher-cybersecurity-standards-2025-01-10/</link><description>根据该命令的草案，总统乔·拜登呼吁在未来几天发布的新行政命令中对联邦机构和承包商实施更严格的网络安全标准，推动旨在解决与中国相关的重复网络操作和网络犯罪活动的改革路透社看到。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 21:16:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/china-hacking-threat-builds-biden-order-tougher-cybersecurity-standards-2025-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国今年有充足的财政空间促进经济增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-has-ample-fiscal-space-bolster-growth-this-year-2025-01-10/</link><description>财政部副部长廖敏周五表示，中国今年有充足的财政政策空间和工具来支持经济增长，并将加大支出刺激投资。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 17:43:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-has-ample-fiscal-space-bolster-growth-this-year-2025-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>英国高级立法者向伦敦证券交易所和监管机构表达了对 Shein 的担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/senior-uk-lawmaker-flags-concerns-about-shein-lse-regulator-2025-01-10/</link><description>英国议会委员会主席周四写信给伦敦证券交易所，对 Shein 代表在本周的听证会上提供的证据表示担忧，并询问交易所如何检查寻求上市的公司的声明。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 17:31:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/senior-uk-lawmaker-flags-concerns-about-shein-lse-regulator-2025-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>沙利文表示，美国已对与中国有关的电信公司网络攻击做出回应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-has-responded-chinese-linked-cyber-attacks-telecoms-firms-sullivan-says-2025-01-10/</link><description>美国国家安全顾问杰克·沙利文周五表示，美国已采取措施应对与中国有关的针对美国电信公司的网络间谍活动。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 15:35:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-has-responded-chinese-linked-cyber-attacks-telecoms-firms-sullivan-says-2025-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>缅甸接连发生电信诈骗事件后，中国警告公民谨防电信诈骗</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-warns-citizens-telecom-fraud-after-reports-scams-myanmar-2025-01-10/</link><description>中国驻缅甸大使馆周五敦促中国公民警惕电信和网络诈骗，此前多起报道称，公民被宣传“高薪海外工作”的网络诈骗引诱到缅甸边境城镇苗瓦迪。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 13:59:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-warns-citizens-telecom-fraud-after-reports-scams-myanmar-2025-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>美国议员要求政府考虑限制向中国军方出口生物技术</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-lawmakers-ask-government-consider-curbs-biotech-exports-chinas-military-2025-01-10/</link><description>一个由两党议员组成的小组呼吁拜登政府考虑限制向中国军方出口美国生物技术，理由是担心北京可能将其武器化以制造更多有毒病原体。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 12:05:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-lawmakers-ask-government-consider-curbs-biotech-exports-chinas-military-2025-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>据美国有线电视新闻网报道，中国黑客入侵了美国外国投资审查机构</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/chinese-hackers-breached-us-govt-office-that-assesses-foreign-investments-2025-01-10/</link><description>据美国有线电视新闻网 (CNN) 周五援引三名知情美国官员的话报道，中国黑客入侵了美国外国投资委员会 (CFIUS)，该委员会是一个审查外国投资是否存在国家安全风险的政府机构。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 11:12:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/chinese-hackers-breached-us-govt-office-that-assesses-foreign-investments-2025-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>最高法院似乎倾向于维持 TikTok 在美国的禁令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/supreme-court-hear-fight-over-looming-us-ban-tiktok-2025-01-10/</link><description>周五，最高法院似乎倾向于维持一项法律，该法律将在 1 月 19 日之前强制在美国出售或禁止流行的短视频应用程序 TikTok，法官们重点关注的是对中国的国家安全担忧，从而引发了此次镇压。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 11:08:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/supreme-court-hear-fight-over-looming-us-ban-tiktok-2025-01-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>